"I
turned
from
them
both,
and
gazing
wearily
round
the
room,
I
saw
two
pictures
set
in
the
oak
panelling
one
on
each
side
the
mantel
piece.
Ceasing
to
take
part
in
the
bantering
conversation
that
flowed
on
between
Mr.
and
Mrs.
Crimsworth,
I
bent
my
