I
presently
recognised
her;
I
had
seen
this
picture
before
in
childhood;
it
was
my
mother;
that
and
the
companion
picture
being
the
only
heir
looms
saved
out
of
the
sale
of
my
father's
property.
"The
face,
I
remembered,
had
pleased
me
as
a
boy,
but
then
I
did
not
understand
it;
now
I
knew
how
rare
that
class
of
face
is
in
the
world,
and
I
appreciated
keenly
