and
I
was
soon
seated
at
it,
and
engaged
in
rendering
the
English
answers
into
German.
A
sentiment
of
keen
pleasure
accompanied
this
first
effort
to
earn
my
own
living
a
sentiment
neither
poisoned
nor
weakened
by
the
presence
of
the
taskmaster,
who
stood
and
watched
me
for
some
