besides,
if
it
were
otherwise,
if
she
be
both
young
and
pretty,
I
am
not
handsome,
and
no
dressing
can
make
me
so,
therefore
I'll
go
as
I
am."
And
off
I
started,
cursorily
glancing
sideways
as
I
passed
the
toilet
table,
surmounted
by
a
looking
glass:
a
thin
irregular
face
I
saw,
with
sunk,
dark
eyes
under
a
large,
square
