for
the
shafts
of
Cupid.
I
was
soon
at
the
entrance
of
the
pensionnat,
in
a
moment
I
had
pulled
the
bell;
in
another
moment
the
door
was
opened,
and
within
appeared
a
passage
paved
alternately
with
black
and
white
marble;
the
walls
were
painted
in
imitation
of
marble
also;
and
at
the
far
end
opened
a
glass
door,
through
