she
now
relinquished
a
faint
prospect
of
pleasant
excitement;
she
had
been
waiting
for
something
to
be
discussed
in
which
she
had
a
degree
of
interest;
the
discussion
was
not
to
come
on,
so
expectation
sank
back,
shrunk
and
sad,
but
attention,
promptly
filling
up
the
void,
repaired
in
a
moment
the
transient
collapse
of
feature;
still,
I
felt,
rather
than
saw,
during
the
whole
course
of
the
