She
hesitated;
she
could
not
hear
the
words
amidst
the
uproar
now
pervading
both
school
rooms;
I
repeated
the
sign;
she
approached;
again
she
paused
within
half
a
yard
of
the
estrade,
and
looked
shy,
and
still
doubtful
whether
she
had
mistaken
