her
with
my
hand
upon
it,
and
a
pencil
in
that
hand,
I
saw
her
moved,
and,
as
it
were,
kindled;
her
depression
beamed
as
a
cloud
might
behind
which
the
sun
is
burning.
"This
devoir
has
numerous
