"Strength
and
rarity!"
I
repeated
to
myself;
"ay,
the
words
are
probably
true,"
for
on
looking
up,
I
saw
the
sun
had
dissevered
its
screening
cloud,
her
countenance
was
transfigured,
a
smile
shone
in
her
eyes
a
smile
almost
triumphant;
it
seemed
to
say
"I
am
glad
you
have
been
forced
to
discover
so
much
of
my
nature;
you
need
not
so
carefully
moderate
